<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - Página no encontrada - <%= appName %></title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 60px 40px;
            max-width: 600px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }
        .emoji {
            font-size: 120px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 72px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 800;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 28px;
        }
        p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .path {
            background: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            color: #667eea;
            font-family: monospace;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            word-break: break-all;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 18px;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .btn-secondary {
            background: white;
            color: #667eea;
            border: 2px solid #667eea;
        }
        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% {
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
            50% {
                transform: translateY(-20px);
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class=>(・﹏・)</div>
        <h1>404</h1>
        <h2>Página no encontrada</h2>
        <p>Lo sentimos, la página que buscas no existe o fue movida.</p>
        
        <% if (locals.path) { %>
            <div class="path">
                Ruta solicitada: <%= path %>
            </div>
        <% } %>
    </div>
</body>
</html>